{"type":"message","id":"58a1e9f4","parentId":"4fd8c144","timestamp":"2026-03-04T14:09:28.851Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-04 22:09:26 GMT+8] Feishu[main] message in group oc_7f69817aaa4ff4c53cc15ea3e4c1f83d: 联网搜索一下 宁做尘土 勿随流水 全词\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55b79f967ca4c4a9f18df899322\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_beb951b5f9e4137501dde4a920879b62\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_7f69817aaa4ff4c53cc15ea3e4c1f83d\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_beb951b5f9e4137501dde4a920879b62\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_7f69817aaa4ff4c53cc15ea3e4c1f83d\",\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_beb951b5f9e4137501dde4a920879b62\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_beb951b5f9e4137501dde4a920879b62\"\n}\n```\n\n联网搜索一下  宁做尘土  勿随流水  全词"}],"timestamp":1772633368849}}
